fields.description:
If you are looking for something special to decorate a boy nursery, then this eco needle felted solar system mobile is for you. You can use this space mobile not only as a baby mobile, but also as educational decor for a kid's room for boys and girls under 12-14 years old. Such a planets mobile is made of 100% sheep wool and has long threads so that you can hang it on any hook at the desired height (hook is not included).

*** Mobile will include:

Once you've chosen a planet style, you can choose what your mobile will include:

*Astronaut: only Solar System + astronaut, without Pluto;
*Astronaut + Pluto: Solar System + astronaut + Pluto;

*Rocket: only Solar System + Rocket, without Pluto;
*Rocket + Pluto: Solar System + Rocket + Pluto;

*Astronaut + Rocket + UFO: only Solar System + Astronaut + Rocket + UFO, without Pluto;
*Astronaut + Rocket + UFO + Pluto: Solar System + Astronaut + Rocket + UFO + Pluto;

*Astronaut + Rocket: only Solar System + Astronaut + Rocket, without Pluto;
*Astronaut + Rocket + Pluto: Solar System + Astronaut + Rocket + Pluto;

***You can also choose a boy/girl or neutral astronaut or rocket for your mobile.
